name: Small Personalised Canvas Print (16x12")
description: Transform your images into a fantastic personalised Canvas Print ... Perhaps you're looking to transform a Holiday Snap, a Wedding Photograph or even your child's first Drawing... whatever the occasion, we are specialists in creating large Canvas Prints from your Digital Photographs, Slides, Negatives, Artwork... just about anything really. Our Canvas Prints have to be seen to be believed. They are printed and finished to the very highest quality, meaning you will be proud to display your chosen masterpiece for years to come. Please let us know via email once you've ordered if you'd like your print Gallery Wrapped (Image wrapped around side), with White Edges, Black Edges or a Colour of your choice. If you have any queries, please call 0845 833 1183 or email hello@ziing.co.uk
